      "id": "PopularPost163529",
      "post_content": "@BetrayerKol  \nthe reasons that combo doesn't work are as follows.  \nA) you can't keep stacking on eon counters because you have to return it to your hand every time you pop the extra turn effect, which removes all extra counters  \nB) even if you could take infinite turns, Maralen of the Mornsong would only be doing damage to you, so you would kill yourself for nothing...  \nso pretty much... yeah, that's about it. it doesn't work that way, and if it did, it would kill you.",
      "posted_by": "CaptainMal",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost163529\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">@BetrayerKol<br/>the reasons that combo doesn't work are as follows.<br/>A) you can't keep stacking on eon counters because you have to return it to your hand every time you pop the extra turn effect, which removes all extra counters<br/>B) even if you could take infinite turns, Maralen of the Mornsong would only be doing damage to you, so you would kill yourself for nothing...<br/>so pretty much... yeah, that's about it. it doesn't work that way, and if it did, it would kill you.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '163529'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy61689\">CaptainMal</span>\r\n                                (5/24/2011 9:31:56 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.